  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >About the game.</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Get ready for a night of pure terror as you step into the shoes of Steve, a security guard on his first shift at a hospital filled with dark secrets. While monitoring the security cameras, you’ll encounter strange anomalies that you must investigate and fix, but not everything is as it seems. With each step, you’ll get closer to uncovering the hospital's dark past and the mystery surrounding your daughter.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use the cameras to track supernatural events in real-time.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3247990/extras/21baf054a1e63887c68d9e0bbe36b733.poster.avif?t=1739981041\" width=712 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3247990/extras/21baf054a1e63887c68d9e0bbe36b733.webm?t=1739981041\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3247990/extras/21baf054a1e63887c68d9e0bbe36b733.mp4?t=1739981041\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >When something goes wrong, act fast: head to the location of the anomaly, investigate, and find a way to fix it before it's too late.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3247990/extras/3d67a2eb68b6598655e54135fc148597.poster.avif?t=1739981041\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3247990/extras/3d67a2eb68b6598655e54135fc148597.webm?t=1739981041\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3247990/extras/3d67a2eb68b6598655e54135fc148597.mp4?t=1739981041\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore the darkest corners of the hospital as you uncover forgotten memories and piece together the truth about your daughter, all while trapped in an oppressive atmosphere where every shadow could be deadly.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3247990/extras/309bd3884b9fd061c5cfe6eebcafb47b.poster.avif?t=1739981041\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3247990/extras/309bd3884b9fd061c5cfe6eebcafb47b.webm?t=1739981041\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3247990/extras/309bd3884b9fd061c5cfe6eebcafb47b.mp4?t=1739981041\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >But remember, you're not alone. Something watches from the shadows. And worse, the nightmares lurking in this hospital are not mere illusions.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3247990/extras/960f7b64da7926109a4c5cba17b484ab.poster.avif?t=1739981041\" width=740 height=416 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3247990/extras/960f7b64da7926109a4c5cba17b484ab.webm?t=1739981041\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3247990/extras/960f7b64da7926109a4c5cba17b484ab.mp4?t=1739981041\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Features.</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Immersive experience:</strong> Atmospheric and photorealistic graphics that intensify the horror experience.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Gameplay:</strong> The game is a walking simulator with anomaly detection mechanics. Unlike other games, you'll have to personally fix the anomalies.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Psychological horror:</strong> The game will try to deceive and scare you.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>From the Other Side </strong>is a short game lasting between 60 and 90 minutes.</p></li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >About the game.</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Get ready for a night of pure terror as you step into the shoes of Steve, a security guard on his first shift at a hospital filled with dark secrets. While monitoring the security cameras, you’ll encounter strange anomalies that you must investigate and fix, but not everything is as it seems. With each step, you’ll get closer to uncovering the hospital's dark past and the mystery surrounding your daughter.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use the cameras to track supernatural events in real-time.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3247990/extras/21baf054a1e63887c68d9e0bbe36b733.poster.avif?t=1739981041\" width=712 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3247990/extras/21baf054a1e63887c68d9e0bbe36b733.webm?t=1739981041\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3247990/extras/21baf054a1e63887c68d9e0bbe36b733.mp4?t=1739981041\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >When something goes wrong, act fast: head to the location of the anomaly, investigate, and find a way to fix it before it's too late.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3247990/extras/3d67a2eb68b6598655e54135fc148597.poster.avif?t=1739981041\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3247990/extras/3d67a2eb68b6598655e54135fc148597.webm?t=1739981041\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3247990/extras/3d67a2eb68b6598655e54135fc148597.mp4?t=1739981041\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore the darkest corners of the hospital as you uncover forgotten memories and piece together the truth about your daughter, all while trapped in an oppressive atmosphere where every shadow could be deadly.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3247990/extras/309bd3884b9fd061c5cfe6eebcafb47b.poster.avif?t=1739981041\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3247990/extras/309bd3884b9fd061c5cfe6eebcafb47b.webm?t=1739981041\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3247990/extras/309bd3884b9fd061c5cfe6eebcafb47b.mp4?t=1739981041\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >But remember, you're not alone. Something watches from the shadows. And worse, the nightmares lurking in this hospital are not mere illusions.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3247990/extras/960f7b64da7926109a4c5cba17b484ab.poster.avif?t=1739981041\" width=740 height=416 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3247990/extras/960f7b64da7926109a4c5cba17b484ab.webm?t=1739981041\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3247990/extras/960f7b64da7926109a4c5cba17b484ab.mp4?t=1739981041\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Features.</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Immersive experience:</strong> Atmospheric and photorealistic graphics that intensify the horror experience.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Gameplay:</strong> The game is a walking simulator with anomaly detection mechanics. Unlike other games, you'll have to personally fix the anomalies.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Psychological horror:</strong> The game will try to deceive and scare you.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>From the Other Side </strong>is a short game lasting between 60 and 90 minutes.</p></li></ul>",
